Class MatchAny

java.lang.Object
koopa.core.parsers.ParserCombinator
koopa.core.grammars.combinators.GrammaticalCombinator
koopa.core.grammars.combinators.MatchAny
public class MatchAny extends GrammaticalCombinator
Accepts any and all tokens. Will only fail when there are no more tokens on the token stream (ignoring separators).
